1 \(L_p\) Minkowski distance measures

\[d_{\textrm{Minkowski}}\left(x,y\right)=\left(\sum _{i=1}^{n}|x_{i}-y_{i}|^{p}\right)^{1/p}\]

1.1 Manhattan distance

p = 1

\[d_{man} = x - y\]

1.2 Euclidean distance

p = 2
